730
01:33:00,160 --> 01:33:01,479
Juniore!

731
01:33:03,720 --> 01:33:05,119
Indi!

732
01:33:13,760 --> 01:33:15,990
O, Bože.

733
01:33:16,120 --> 01:33:17,678
Izgubio sam ga.

734
01:33:21,640 --> 01:33:23,949
A nikada mu nisam ništa rekao.

735
01:33:26,360 --> 01:33:28,430
Jednostavno nisam bio spreman.

736
